{
  "name": "Show Car Concours",
  "description": "Concours d'Elegance level presentation. Deep monochrome gloss body, every trim piece polished chrome, piano black undercarriage, gold mirror badging, pearl highlight on fender caps. No sponsors, no numbers — only the paint.",
  "author": "Shokker Paint Booth",
  "version": "6.2.0",
  "compatible_with": "any restored classic, pre-war luxury, 50s-70s restorations, concours builds",
  "notes": "Concours is about DEPTH. baseSpecStrength stays at 1 on body so reflections stack cleanly. If the car is photographed indoors, drop chrome tolerance to 25 to avoid chrome leaking into dark body paint.",
